		"description": "<p>By focusing on a creature of intelligence 3 or higher within 30ft you can attempt to read its mind as an action. On the first round you pick up any surface thoughts but do not alert the creature to your intrusion. On the second round and any following round you may attempt to locate a specific thought or memory, which causes the target to make a Wisdom save. On a successful save the target becomes aware you are in their mind and the connection is broken, but on a failed save you locate the specific thought or memory. You may use this Noetic once per short or long rest.</p>",
